```{r pancreas 32445859, include=FALSE}

PMID_32445859 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32445859', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32445859 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32445859$eprint)

doi_32445859 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32445859$doi)
```
